      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1750803933327,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional\n- Scan Outlook emails for specific emails \n(either keyword filtering or hasAttachment)\n- Extract email body and attachments\n- Push content to S3, metadata to postgres\n- Fetches new emails once every 15 minutes \n(when activated)\n\nNon-functional\n- Scalable to multiple user accounts\n- Secure authentication and data transmission\n- Retry logic in case of failures\n- Logging & monitoring\n- Batch processes",
      "fontSize": 26.401256055017285,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional\n- Scan Outlook emails for specific emails \n(either keyword filtering or hasAttachment)\n- Extract email body and attachments\n- Push content to S3, metadata to postgres\n- Fetches new emails once every 15 minutes \n(when activated)\n\nNon-functional\n- Scalable to multiple user accounts\n- Secure authentication and data transmission\n- Retry logic in case of failures\n- Logging & monitoring\n- Batch processes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
